{"tid":294395,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[美漫分享] 神奇女俠 一人的正義聯盟 JLA: A League of One","createTime":"2017-06-23T02:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T19:26:12.000Z","uid":121471,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc021d851c1b84ee1cbe5ead6ac0ac510aafc0a","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"[美漫分享] 神奇女俠經典 一人的正義聯盟 JLA: A League of One<br />\n神奇女俠經典既故事唔多,亦冇乜人睇冇乜人講.<br />\n今次自推一個我個人排頭三既故事.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/6zuqLy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F6zuqLy.jpg&h=ea1edc7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJLA: A League of One<br />\nNovember, 2000<br />\nWriters, Pencilers: Christopher Moeller<br />\n故事大概:<br />\nDiana由古老希臘先知聽到一個預言, 得知JL將會因為對抗古老惡龍而最終與對方同歸於盡.<br />\n為左避免自己既朋友同埋世界上最重要既英雄犧牲, Diana決定獨自去應付惡龍."},{"pid":"c94a068b45f9807726847bbf191153fdd970eb3c","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"呢個故事精彩在睇到WW點&quot;對付&quot;全隊JL.<br />\n聽到預言後Diana非常不安亦無心開會,<br />\n因為佢明白如果要救所有隊友, 就無可避免要首先傷害佢地.<br />\n於JLA會議中Diana聽到應該係同惡龍有關既資料,<br />\n但係為左保護隊友佢選擇隱瞞.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/k7oVEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fk7oVEw.jpg&h=52851de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會議完結後各人開始執行任務, Batman當然已經發現Diana有異樣.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Kt4RGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FKt4RGd.jpg&h=28b0d741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDiana第一個搞掂J'onn先, 用Lasso of Truth將佢變返真身,<br />\n之後再用JLA月球Watchtower既傳送器將佢送去一個佢無辦法脫身既地方, 火山.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/0TISV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F0TISV2.jpg&h=9f3a1727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKyle因為收唔到J'onn既通訊而返Watchtower.<br />\nDiana簡單就分左佢心&amp;#25886;埋介指, 再將佢擊暈.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/1wiuZt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F1wiuZt.jpg&h=e01a0394&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5eb93ace89e3decf9392616b0e7459f80c3e2dcb","tid":294395,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"留名睇野"},{"pid":"4b959aee3bb78a8a00325610469163623d5c3f01","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"Diana將Aquaman拋入一個就算係佢都好困難先可以逃出既漩渦.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/i4Nktr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fi4Nktr.jpg&h=eef2f931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透過樹精幫助Diana亦成功收拾Flash.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/cKOw12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FcKOw12.jpg&h=c3f7bb91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開始已經察覺到Diana有異樣既Batman捉到樹精<br />\n樹精亦將預言一事和盤托出.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/a8jZVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fa8jZVB.jpg&h=29458bd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6947a36a3a1a125553a599f47f94ff779fb21c26","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:48:12.000Z","msg":"返到Watchtower既Diana被尾隨既Batman阻止.<br />\n知道晒所有事既Batman絕不認同Diana獨自解決既做法.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Em6tri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FEm6tri.jpg&h=a66b5686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過一番邊理論邊打鬥後Diana更不惜破壞教宗送俾JLA既禮物顯示決心.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/ijCFNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FijCFNA.jpg&h=fad2ab96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後當然都能夠成功擊倒Batman.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/oXZiH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FoXZiH4.jpg&h=5e6298bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/RHtQ89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FRHtQ89.jpg&h=d6474809&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f87bf2f6c9830c2ecc0ef0b33ad8b8234b6e1e1","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"Diana將三個暈左既隊友放入太空倉再送出太空.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/o8dlSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fo8dlSc.jpg&h=9b737998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到地球既Diana聯絡Superman見面.<br />\n再出奇不意地展開攻擊.<br />\nClark當然唔會輕易就範.<br />\n短短四頁打鬥非常精彩.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/x49JXf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fx49JXf.jpg&h=6cd1e796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/0tPEvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F0tPEvz.jpg&h=00899cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDiana終於向Clark坦白.<br />\n佢將三個隊友送向太陽附近, 被過千個類似物件包圍.<br />\n而太空倉仲有12個鐘氧氣供應.<br />\nDiana雖然唔可以打低Clark, 但係打傷佢就會令佢冇咁快救到其他隊友.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/n6CGco.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fn6CGco.jpg&h=ce50c4ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預言既事Clark亦都知道, 而呢個時候惡龍更加已經開始攻擊平民.<br />\nClark如果同Diana一齊打龍就會救唔到其他隊友.<br />\nDiana明白佢咁做會令Clark非常難受, 但係世界唔能夠失去Superman.<br />\n最後Clark當然立刻飛向太空救隊友.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/7y82ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F7y82ba.jpg&h=cd2a4cef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c578b04bfe1c20e327133215c8d3fd8d00a79d4","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"Diana如願獨自前去對付惡龍.<br />\n經過一番打鬥同追逐後去到惡龍既山洞.<br />\n惡龍以火炎攻擊Diana.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/P5OVy7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FP5OVy7.jpg&h=390aaf0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n惡龍噴出既並唔係普通火炎.<br />\n而係會將欺騙, 謊言既人燃燒.<br />\n但係卻唔足夠殺死Diana.<br />\nDiana堅定既純潔令佢可以克服呢d火炎.<br />\n佢更加肯定一直既行動係正確, 因為JLA其他成員好可能不敵呢種火炎.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/QzxYLw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FQzxYLw.jpg&h=1b0a1c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n惡龍對Diana能夠絲毫無損感到難以置信.<br />\nDiana表示佢相信真相, 同情.<br />\n所以佢並唔想殺死惡龍,<br />\n佢希望惡龍能夠交出弱點心臟俾佢保管作為保証唔會再作惡.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/LgonMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FLgonMj.jpg&h=87b14e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Ol3716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FOl3716.jpg&h=6852b286&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71b7928fed8c5bbb3e977edcfa1c28fcc4ba64af","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"惡龍假裝接受Diana既建議, 等Diana鬆懈就攻擊再帶住弱點心臟飛走.<br />\nDiana追上去再用以克服慌言既Lasso of Truth索住惡龍.<br />\n但係卻受到惡龍既毒氣攻擊.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NLplhu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNLplhu.jpg&h=da488089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受到毒氣影響Diana開始轉化成怪物.<br />\nAmazon戰士既一面&amp;#21946;毒氣影響下完全駕馭Diana.<br />\n接住就一擊將惡龍既心臟擊破, 惡龍因此灰飛煙滅.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/9jE6cX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F9jE6cX.jpg&h=fdee9cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然擊倒惡龍後Diana回復正常, 但係失去意識落入大海.<br />\n接近死亡既Diana一路沉入大海深處, 直到Superman趕到將佢帶回地面.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/cldSip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FcldSip.jpg&h=ee670421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他JLA隊友亦黎到, Superman努力拯救下, Diana終於甦醒.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/YPtG4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FYPtG4T.jpg&h=bcf0db79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4e4be7177e7eabd8dfcc02e74a1a8cb172dcbfe","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:52:25.000Z","msg":"Diana向Clark解釋自己既決定.<br />\n雖然傷害到所有人, 但係呢個決定係佢必需要做.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4ozgk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4ozgk.jpg&h=6aaaf6db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDiana反問Clark如果件事發生&amp;#21946;佢身上會點做.<br />\nClark初頭話自己會同隊友一齊戰死,<br />\n但係最後都承認佢會做出同Diana相同既決定.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/d509pY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fd509pY.jpg&h=da3ed5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nClark表示Diana的確傷左佢心, 希望Diana保證唔會再發生相同既事.<br />\nDiana表示JLA係佢家人, 佢只會做佢必需要做既去保護佢地.<br />\n呢樣係Diana唯一可以保證既事.<br />\n最後JLA終於團結返一齊.<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NGPUSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNGPUSj.jpg&h=b05f7f2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c43adfebda38fa079a91c504292c9010bdae70e","tid":294395,"uid":16904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"留"},{"pid":"cd76d4b5b2f258105d3fab0caca2a13375138712","tid":294395,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:57:00.000Z","msg":"早兩年DC出過新版，要買唔難<br />\n<br />\n<ins><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Justice-League-One-Jla-America/dp/1401258239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FJustice-League-One-Jla-America%2Fdp%2F1401258239&d=2fYxIhFQhlO8Y94OsLuIXb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=9bb0ecf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Justice-League-One-Jla-America/dp/1401258239</a> </ins><br />\n合訂本: Justice League: A League of One <br />\n出版年份: 2015, ISBN: 9781401258238 <br />\n收錄: JLA: A LEAGUE OF ONE, JUSTICE LEAGUE: COLD STEEL #1-2."},{"pid":"ee5e9d13c4990c9d056e1139a9e188cefecb64c3","tid":294395,"uid":18818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"小智巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631ecd25d1467e40e22024873bb19d6640c99b9f","tid":294395,"uid":18818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20